      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781857533,
      "updated": 1781857533
    },
    {
      "id": "6a34efe900000000000bb8f9",
      "text": "\t現時点（2026/6/19）の状態",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781854186,
      "updated": 1781857123
    },
    {
      "id": "6a34f06300000000000bb901",
      "text": "\tスクリーンショット",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781854307,
      "updated": 1781856911
    },
    {
      "id": "6a34f06b00000000000bb902",
      "text": "\t\t[[https://gyazo.com/56a831ee57637bf9cf82e245cef1fd62]]",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781854316,
      "updated": 1781857082
    },
    {
      "id": "6a34fa96000000000081652f",
      "text": "\t\t[[https://gyazo.com/df439d59de54547d4c60d68500ab33bf]]",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781856918,
      "updated": 1781857095
    },
    {
      "id": "6a35023f000000000042d25f",
      "text": "  スタイルは揃っていると感じるが、個人的には細い線（最初のバージョン）で揃える方が好きかも[yosider.icon]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1781858880,
      "updated": 1781930842
    },
    {
      "id": "6a361ba6000000000074cbdd",
      "text": "   [https://gyazo.com/037a749eea2468dd2be8e87a1d99300f]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1781930916,
      "updated": 1781930917
    },
    {
      "id": "6a361b26000000000074cbdb",
      "text": "   細いほうがスタイリッシュな感じがする",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1781930788,
      "updated": 1781930926
    },
    {
      "id": "6a361b2b000000000074cbdc",
      "text": "   変更範囲が既存記法にまで及んでいる気持ち悪さがある",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1781930793,
      "updated": 1781930858
    },
    {
      "id": "6a368a4e00000000005acd2a",
      "text": "   　わかる[Nrem.icon]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1781959247,
      "updated": 1781959266
    },
    {
      "id": "6a361bbe000000000074cbdf",
      "text": "   色の調整もされているんだな",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1781930940,
      "updated": 1781930994
    },
    {
      "id": "6a36d9d900000000003d3f7a",
      "text": "   　線を1pxにすると配色が判別しづらくなる問題があり…[Nrem.icon]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1781979610,
      "updated": 1781979803
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3688a800000000005acd25",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1781958825,
      "updated": 1781962857
    },
    {
      "id": "6a367fd800000000005acd15",
      "text": " table:引用ブロックとインライン引用の対照表（一般）",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1781956569,
      "updated": 1781958918
    },
    {
      "id": "6a367fd800000000005acd16",
      "text": " 　\t引用ブロック記法\tインライン引用記法",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1781956569,
      "updated": 1781962878
    },
    {
      "id": "6a367fd800000000005acd17",
      "text": " 　書式の対象\t行全体\t段落内（インライン要素）",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1781956569,
      "updated": 1781960877
    },
    {
      "id": "6a367fd800000000005acd18",
      "text": " 　スケール感\tひとまとまり\t部分的、局所的、文の一部",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1781956569,
      "updated": 1781971387
    },
    {
      "id": "6a367fd800000000005acd19",
      "text": " 　引用の基本単位\t文章。一行から複数の段落\t一語句、一節、一段落。ピンポイントの抜粋",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1781956569,
      "updated": 1781971409
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3685cf00000000005acd20",
      "text": " 　実際の使われ方\t\t直接の言及箇所を提示するのに用いられることが多い",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1781958096,
      "updated": 1781961156
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3684f400000000005acd1f",
      "text": " 　マーカー\t行頭の区切り線（左側）/ 1px (default) ＋字下げ\t–",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1781957877,
      "updated": 1781979945
    },
    {
      "id": "6a36834b00000000005acd1d",
      "text": " 　余白\t行末に偏在（右側）\t–",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1781957452,
      "updated": 1781958918
    },
    {
      "id": "6a36839b00000000005acd1e",
      "text": " 　導線、重心\t行頭の区切り線（左側） / 左寄せ\t–",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1781957532,
      "updated": 1781979879
    },
    {
      "id": "6a350245000000000042d260",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1781858885,
      "updated": 1781958906
    },
    {
      "id": "6a36974500000000005acd44",
      "text": "　斜体式",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1781962566,
      "updated": 1781963217
    },
    {
      "id": "6a36bd3800000000001ec60e",
      "text": "　　これ、私が書いてしまってもいいのだろうか…？[Nrem.icon]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1781972281,
      "updated": 1781972367
    },
    {
      "id": "6a36d54a00000000003d3f63",
      "text": "　　前景要素による差別化",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1781978443,
      "updated": 1781978454
    },
    {
      "id": "6a36d5d200000000003d3f72",
      "text": "　　　斜体と左上の引用符アイコンによって通常テキストと異なることが明瞭に示される",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1781978579,
      "updated": 1781978663
    },
    {
      "id": "6a36d62900000000003d3f73",
      "text": "　　テキストの視認性",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1781978666,
      "updated": 1781978692
    },
    {
      "id": "6a36d64900000000003d3f74",
      "text": "　　　[/ 斜体]と[/ italic]は立体と比較してテキストの視認性・判読性・可読性が低い",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1781978698,
      "updated": 1781978828
    },
    {
      "id": "6a36d6ce00000000003d3f75",
      "text": "　　　多くの日本語フォントは斜体に対応していない。この場合、日本語組版のマス目をレンダラー側で菱形状に変形する形で描画される",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1781978831,
      "updated": 1781979092
    },
    {
      "id": "6a36d7ce00000000003d3f78",
      "text": "　　　　現在の標準的な閲覧環境では",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1781979087,
      "updated": 1781979098
    },
    {
      "id": "6a36974500000000005acd45",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1781962566,
      "updated": 1781962566
    },
    {
      "id": "6a36892a00000000005acd29",
      "text": "　下線式の設計思想（by [Nrem.icon]）",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1781958955,
      "updated": 1781971970
    },
    {
      "id": "6a367f7500000000005acd03",
      "text": "  table:対照表",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1781956470,
      "updated": 1781958952
    },
    {
      "id": "6a367f7500000000005acd04",
      "text": "  　\t引用ブロック\tインライン引用（下線式）",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1781956470,
      "updated": 1781972194
    },
    {
      "id": "6a367f7500000000005acd08",
      "text": "  　font\tnormal (default)\tsmaller (BIZ UDゴシック / weight 400 - 450)",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1781956470,
      "updated": 1781963637
    },
    {
      "id": "6a367f7500000000005acd09",
      "text": "  　マーカー\t行頭の区切り線（左側/中程度の太さ\t下線/細め × 引用符アイコン",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1781956470,
      "updated": 1781979920
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3691d600000000005acd33",
      "text": "  　\t（想定値 3px - 3.5px 程度）\t（想定幅 2px - 2.5px）",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1781961175,
      "updated": 1781972215
    },
    {
      "id": "6a367f7500000000005acd0a",
      "text": "  　余白\t行末全体に偏在（右側）\t通常テキストとの境界（左右、引用符アイコンの領域（左））、上端（わずか）",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1781956470,
      "updated": 1781972462
    },
    {
      "id": "6a367f7500000000005acd0b",
      "text": "  　導線、重心\t行頭方向 / 左寄せ\t段落のベースライン（下方向） / テキストの流れる方向",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1781956470,
      "updated": 1781963329
    },
    {
      "id": "6a36d5ad00000000003d3f70",
      "text": "  主にスケール感の違いと後景要素による差別化",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1781978542,
      "updated": 1781978568
    },
    {
      "id": "6a36d5ad00000000003d3f71",
      "text": "  　",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1781978542,
      "updated": 1781978542
    },
    {
      "id": "6a367f7500000000005acd0d",
      "text": "  インライン引用記法の寸法比",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1781956470,
      "updated": 1781963872
    },
    {
      "id": "6a367f7500000000005acd0f",
      "text": "  　余白（padding,  逆凹状）：",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1781956470,
      "updated": 1781979157
    },
    {
      "id": "6a36d34800000000003d3f56",
      "text": "  　　`引用符アイコンの領域（左側）≧ 上側の余白（BG）> 下線の幅 ≒ 引用符アイコンの太さ ≒ 下線の幅＋左右それぞれの余白`",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1781977928,
      "updated": 1781979291
    },
    {
      "id": "6a367f7500000000005acd10",
      "text": "  　サイズ感：",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1781956470,
      "updated": 1781977959
    },
    {
      "id": "6a36d35400000000003d3f57",
      "text": "  　　`引用ブロックのスケール感 > インライン引用のスケール感`",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1781977941,
      "updated": 1781977941
    },
    {
      "id": "6a36d37e00000000003d3f58",
      "text": "  　　この考え方が border の幅の違いにも関係している",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1781977982,
      "updated": 1781978039
    },
    {
      "id": "6a36ba5b00000000001ec5fe",
      "text": " 　引用ブロックとインライン引用の配色の統一",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1781971547,
      "updated": 1781971547
    },
    {
      "id": "6a36ba5e00000000001ec5ff",
      "text": " 　　インライン引用記法の「下線」の処理：",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1781971550,
      "updated": 1781978282
    },
    {
      "id": "6a36d4a900000000003d3f5d",
      "text": " 　　　後景要素の一部分として表示する必要がある",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1781978282,
      "updated": 1781978294
    },
    {
      "id": "6a36d45500000000003d3f5c",
      "text": " 　　　仮に文字色（前景要素）と同じ色にすると「強調マーカー」にしか見えなくなってしまう（[_ 強調マーカー]に見える問題）",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1781978198,
      "updated": 1781978214
    },
    {
      "id": "6a36914500000000005acd32",
      "text": "  　　BGとの明暗コントラストを抑える必要がある",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1781961030,
      "updated": 1781962956
    },
    {
      "id": "6a36934300000000005acd3c",
      "text": "  　　 要素が小さいほど大きなコントラストが必要になる。",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1781961540,
      "updated": 1781978159
    },
    {
      "id": "6a36d42e00000000003d3f5b",
      "text": "  　　 　border 1px では面積が零に近しいため、明暗コントラストの下限が高い",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1781978159,
      "updated": 1781978257
    },
    {
      "id": "6a36d4e800000000003d3f60",
      "text": "　  引用ブロック：border が色を識別可能な程度の太さである必要がある",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1781978344,
      "updated": 1781978344
    },
    {
      "id": "6a36d4e800000000003d3f61",
      "text": "  　　defaultは文字色と同じ無彩色の 1px の区切り線であり、視覚的な面積が零に等しい",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1781978344,
      "updated": 1781978344
    },
    {
      "id": "6a36d4fa00000000003d3f62",
      "text": "  　　Cosenseの 1px border は他のプラットフォームではほとんど見かけない幅であり、1px から 3px への変更は一瞬で見慣れるのではないか",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1781978362,
      "updated": 1781978362
    },
    {
      "id": "6a36952800000000005acd3e",
      "text": " 　　　BGの明度をdefalutから変更するよりも、borderの幅を1pxより大きくするほうが変更のハードルが低い",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1781962024,
      "updated": 1781978358
    },
    {
      "id": "6a367f5a00000000005acd01",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1781956443,
      "updated": 1781956443
    },
    {
      "id": "6a36bb1300000000001ec60b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1781971732,
      "updated": 1781971732
    },
    {
      "id": "6a36bb1300000000001ec60c",
      "text": "[引用記法]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1781971732,
      "updated": 1781971742
    },
    {
      "id": "6a36bae300000000001ec600",
      "text": " code:2026-06-19-1.css",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1781971684,
      "updated": 1781971706
    },
    {
      "id": "6a36bae300000000001ec601",
      "text": "  html {",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1781971684,
      "updated": 1781971684
    },
    {
      "id": "6a36bae300000000001ec602",
      "text": "   \t--quote-border-color: light-dark(hsl(216 10% 75%), hsl(196 10% 43%));",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1781971684,
      "updated": 1781971684
    },
    {
      "id": "6a36bae300000000001ec603",
      "text": "  \t--quote-border-width: 3.5px;",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1781971684,
      "updated": 1781971684
    },
    {
      "id": "6a36bae300000000001ec604",
      "text": "  \t--inline-quote-border-width: 2px;",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1781971684,
      "updated": 1781971684
    },
    {
      "id": "6a36bae300000000001ec605",
      "text": "  }",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1781971684,
      "updated": 1781971684
    },
    {
      "id": "6a36bae300000000001ec606",
      "text": "  .line .quote {",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1781971684,
      "updated": 1781971684
    },
    {
      "id": "6a36bae300000000001ec607",
      "text": "  \tborder-left: solid var(--quote-border-width, 1px)  var(--quote-border-color, #a0a0a0);",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1781971684,
      "updated": 1781971684
    },
    {
      "id": "6a36bae300000000001ec608",
      "text": "  \tbackground-color: var(--quote-bg-color, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05));",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1781971684,
      "updated": 1781971684
    },
    {
      "id": "6a36bae300000000001ec609",
      "text": "  }",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1781971684,
      "updated": 1781971684
    },
    {
      "id": "6a36bb0200000000001ec60a",
      "text": "[インライン引用記法]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1781971715,
      "updated": 1781971726
    },
    {
      "id": "6a34f00a00000000000bb8fb",
      "text": "\tcode:2026-06-19-1.css",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781854267,
      "updated": 1781858880
    },
    {
      "id": "6a34f01700000000000bb8fc",
      "text": "\t\t@import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=BIZ+UDGothic:wght@400;700&display=swap');",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781854267,
      "updated": 1781854490
    },
    {
      "id": "6a34f11a00000000000bb90b",
      "text": "  html {",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781854490,
      "updated": 1781854490
    },
    {
      "id": "6a34f11a00000000000bb90c",
      "text": "  \t--inline-quote-font-family: \"Roboto\", Helvetica, Arial, \"BIZ UDゴシック\", \"BIZ UDGothic\", \"Hiragino Sans\";",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781854490,
      "updated": 1781854490
    },
    {
      "id": "6a34f11a00000000000bb90d",
      "text": "  \t--inline-quote-font-size-adjust: 0.51;",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781854490,
      "updated": 1781854490
    },
    {
      "id": "6a34f11a00000000000bb90e",
      "text": "  }",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781854490,
      "updated": 1781854490
    },
    {
      "id": "6a34f11a00000000000bb90f",
      "text": "  .deco-\\\" {",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781854490,
      "updated": 1781854490
    },
    {
      "id": "6a34f11a00000000000bb910",
      "text": "  \t.line & {",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781854490,
      "updated": 1781854490
    },
    {
      "id": "6a34f11a00000000000bb911",
      "text": "  \t\tvertical-align: baseline;",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781854490,
      "updated": 1781854490
    },
    {
      "id": "6a34f11a00000000000bb912",
      "text": "  \t\tbox-sizing: content-box; /* padding: 5.5px 4.5px 0.5px 2px; */",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781854490,
      "updated": 1781854490
    },
    {
      "id": "6a34f11a00000000000bb913",
      "text": "  \t\tpadding: 5.5px 4px 1px 2px;",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781854490,
      "updated": 1781854490
    },
    {
      "id": "6a34f11a00000000000bb914",
      "text": "  \t\tborder-bottom: solid var(--inline-quote-border-width, var(--quote-border-width, 1px)) var(--quote-border-color, #a0a0a0);",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781854490,
      "updated": 1781854490
    },
    {
      "id": "6a34f11a00000000000bb915",
      "text": "   \t\tbackground-color: var(--quote-bg-color, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05));",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781854490,
      "updated": 1781854490
    },
    {
      "id": "6a34f11a00000000000bb916",
      "text": "  \t\tcolor: var(--quote-text-color, var(--page-text-color, inherit));",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781854490,
      "updated": 1781854490
    },
    {
      "id": "6a34f11a00000000000bb917",
      "text": "  \t\tfont-size: .94em;",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781854490,
      "updated": 1781854490
    },
    {
      "id": "6a34f11a00000000000bb918",
      "text": "   \t\t/* font-weight: var(--inline-quote-font-weight, var(--quote-font-weight, 450)); */",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781854490,
      "updated": 1781854490
    },
    {
      "id": "6a34f11a00000000000bb919",
      "text": "   \t\tfont-family: var(--inline-quote-font-family, var(--page-font-family, \"\")), var(--icons, \"AppIcons\"), sans-serif;",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781854490,
      "updated": 1781854490
    },
    {
      "id": "6a34f11a00000000000bb91a",
      "text": "   \t\t/* font-feature-settings: var(--inline-quote-font-feature-settings, var(--quote-font-feature-settings)); */",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781854490,
      "updated": 1781854490
    },
    {
      "id": "6a34f11a00000000000bb91b",
      "text": "   \t\tfont-size-adjust: var(--inline-quote-font-size-adjust);",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781854490,
      "updated": 1781854490
    },
    {
      "id": "6a34f11a00000000000bb91c",
      "text": "  \t}",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781854490,
      "updated": 1781854490
    },
    {
      "id": "6a34f11a00000000000bb91d",
      "text": "  \t.line &::before {",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781854490,
      "updated": 1781854490
    },
    {
      "id": "6a34f11a00000000000bb91e",
      "text": "  \t\tcontent: \"\\f10e\";",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781854490,
      "updated": 1781854490
    },
    {
      "id": "6a34f11a00000000000bb91f",
      "text": "  \t\tmargin-right: 2px;",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781854490,
      "updated": 1781854490
    },
    {
      "id": "6a34f11a00000000000bb920",
      "text": "  \t\t/* vertical-align: baseline; */",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781854490,
      "updated": 1781854490
    },
    {
      "id": "6a34f11a00000000000bb921",
      "text": "  \t\tvertical-align: super;\tline-height: calc(1em / 0.7);",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781854490,
      "updated": 1781854490
    },
    {
      "id": "6a34f11a00000000000bb922",
      "text": "  \t\tfont-size: .7em; font-style: normal;",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781854490,
      "updated": 1781854490
    },
    {
      "id": "6a34f11a00000000000bb923",
      "text": "  \t\tfont-family: var(--icons, \"Font Awesome 5 Free\", \"Font Awesome 5 Brand\", AppIcons); font-weight: 700;",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781854490,
      "updated": 1781854490
    },
    {
      "id": "6a34f11a00000000000bb924",
      "text": "  \t\tcolor: var(--quote-border-color, #a0a0a0);",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781854490,
      "updated": 1781854490
    },
    {
      "id": "6a34f11a00000000000bb925",
      "text": "  \t}",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781854490,
      "updated": 1781854490
    },
    {
      "id": "6a34f11a00000000000bb926",
      "text": "  \t.line.cursor-line &::before {",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781854490,
      "updated": 1781854490
    },
    {
      "id": "6a34f11a00000000000bb927",
      "text": "  \t\tdisplay: none;",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781854490,
      "updated": 1781854490
    },
    {
      "id": "6a34f11a00000000000bb928",
      "text": "  \t}",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781854490,
      "updated": 1781854490
    },
    {
